definition: surname Mi/name of an ancient state
woods/forest/CL:片[pian4]/circle(s) (i.e. specific group of people)/a collection (of similar things)

sentences.english: The dense forest screened the guerrillas' movements.
sentences.chinese: 密林掩护了游击队员的行动。

sentences.english: They cut out a path through the jungle.
sentences.chinese: 他们在密林中开出了一条小路。

sentences.english: The jungle was creeping back to its old strongholds.
sentences.chinese: 莽丛密林一步一步地蔓延到了古老的城堡。

sentences.english: Soldiers are now sleeping rough in dense jungle.
sentences.chinese: 这个旅的士兵现在密林中露宿。

sentences.english: Today, they can only be found in the deepest mountainous forest areas.
sentences.chinese: 现在也只能在深山密林中才偶尔见到牠的芳踪。

sentences.english: This is a clear through the dense forest in romantic fairy tale elves in the south.
sentences.chinese: 这清楚是一个穿行在浪漫密林的南国童话精灵。

sentences.english: Pavements are soon cracked by weeds and streets overgrown.
sentences.chinese: 杂草在水泥人行道上挤出裂缝生长，街道都变成密林。

sentences.english: On every hand was a charming view of rocky buttresses and wooded heights.
sentences.chinese: 到处是山石嶙峋，密林峰巅，景色迷人。

sentences.english: They are all remote mountains and thick forests, almost no ways to go.
sentences.chinese: 那里几乎是深山密林，有些地方没有人走的。

sentences.english: Tigers live in the thick forests and small animals in the forests are tigers' food.
sentences.chinese: 老虎生活在密林里，以森林中妁小动物为食。

sentences.english: Meereenese seldom rode within their city walls.
sentences.chinese: 密林人绝少在城墙内骑马。

sentences.english: The ho chi minh trail was hacked through jungles covering the southern half of laos .
sentences.chinese: 所谓胡志明小道是在老挝南部的密林中开辟出来的。

sentences.english: They hewed their way through dense jungle.
sentences.chinese: 他们在密林里开辟出一条路。

sentences.english: As night fell, she ran out of the castle, Jingzhi Zhao walked the dense forests.
sentences.chinese: 夜幕降临时，她跑出城堡，径直朝密林中走去。

sentences.english: The path slants the lawn to the depths of the woods.
sentences.chinese: 小径斜穿草地通到了密林深处。

sentences.english: A lovely young woman carrying firewood on her back was walking through lush forest.
sentences.chinese: 一位年轻可人的女子正背着柴禾，穿行在密林中。

definition: Shulin city in New Taipei City 新北市[Xin1 bei3 shi4], Taiwan
